7cc1fdf5-150a-4f25-975f-3c3791f861ea.title: Wydin
7cc1fdf5-150a-4f25-975f-3c3791f861ea.text:
Welcome to my food store!
Would you like to buy anything?

1bbd5ac9-6876-47ae-aefa-ceba16363dcd.title: Note
1bbd5ac9-6876-47ae-aefa-ceba16363dcd.text:
Pirate's Treasure Stage after packing bananas 
in Karamja and sent to Wydins Store.

options.text: Can I get a job here?

6b388c37-7cc5-49a4-9528-b832df813e03.title: Wydin
6b388c37-7cc5-49a4-9528-b832df813e03.text:
Well, you're keen, I'll give you that. Okay, I'll
give you a go. Have you got your own white apron?

4cb12db3-b937-418a-a5ab-403397e4c4d3.title: Note
4cb12db3-b937-418a-a5ab-403397e4c4d3.text: Will need Pirate's Treasure in game to finish dialogue.

f26e9b0b-b7dc-4bb6-a6ec-8eb88c9faade.title: Wydin
f26e9b0b-b7dc-4bb6-a6ec-8eb88c9faade.text:
We have this really exotic fruit all the way from
Karamja. It's called a banana.

options.text: Hmm, I think I'll try one.
I don't like the sound of that.

601f65f8-3085-4001-9ced-8f8da45cc7c6.title: <player>
601f65f8-3085-4001-9ced-8f8da45cc7c6.text: Hmm, I think I'll try one.

3d741f8d-7965-40ad-be8d-5d926d3c471b.title: <player>
3d741f8d-7965-40ad-be8d-5d926d3c471b.text: I don't like the sound of that.

5a18649b-13ce-4797-a67d-8dfecc68d038.title: Wydin
5a18649b-13ce-4797-a67d-8dfecc68d038.text:
Great. You might as well take a look at the rest
of my wares as well.

6a42765c-ce4e-40c8-b6a5-62a11d2c7f46.title: Wydin
6a42765c-ce4e-40c8-b6a5-62a11d2c7f46.text: Well, it's your choice, but I do recommend them.

12108a11-9027-4d1b-a063-ad6677432074.title: <player>
12108a11-9027-4d1b-a063-ad6677432074.text: Can I get a job here?

51936862-4a38-40db-82c1-18fc3d311a83.title: Wydin
51936862-4a38-40db-82c1-18fc3d311a83.text:
Well, you can't work here unless you have a white
apron. Health and safety regulations,
you understand.

1750988e-80c3-4da4-8322-27fa592fe93f.title: <player>
1750988e-80c3-4da4-8322-27fa592fe93f.text: Where can I get one of those?

de38ed7f-71e7-4ed6-b73f-dab22829c6d3.title: Wydin
de38ed7f-71e7-4ed6-b73f-dab22829c6d3.text:
Well, I get all of mine over at the clothing shop
in Varrock. They sell them cheap there.

bad8b680-7724-499f-9936-e4605928257b.title: Wydin
bad8b680-7724-499f-9936-e4605928257b.text:
Oh, and I'm sure that I've seen a spare one over
in Gerrant's fish store somewhere. It's the little
place just north of here.

2ad5ae7c-0feb-4add-87b9-3e80994d7e5e.title: <player>
2ad5ae7c-0feb-4add-87b9-3e80994d7e5e.text: Yes, I have one right here.

c09092a1-bbd8-4c88-9ec4-30fdf61646fa.title: Wydin
c09092a1-bbd8-4c88-9ec4-30fdf61646fa.text:
Wow - you are well prepared! You're hired. Go
through to the back and tidy up for me, please.

aad407f4-50ee-41c4-abad-97535ed6baf7.title: Wydin
aad407f4-50ee-41c4-abad-97535ed6baf7.text: Is it nice and tidy round the back now?

options.text: Yes, can I work out front now?
Yes, are you going to pay me yet?

4da201e1-a3db-4a20-b6a6-a76604abc5ff.title: Wydin
4da201e1-a3db-4a20-b6a6-a76604abc5ff.text: Ah well, it'll give you something to do, won't it.

ae9b41de-86cf-483a-92c9-a1e1a3192348.title: <player>
ae9b41de-86cf-483a-92c9-a1e1a3192348.text: Yes, are you going to pay me yet?

830958e5-642e-4b07-8b7c-fb3cb26f36dc.title: <player>
830958e5-642e-4b07-8b7c-fb3cb26f36dc.text: Yes, can I work out front now?

365c5984-637a-4e3c-94b7-3832a39a4503.title: Wydin
365c5984-637a-4e3c-94b7-3832a39a4503.text: No, I'm the one who works here.

8bc26b18-9dc2-4555-b59c-3de4d4e73d94.title: Wydin
8bc26b18-9dc2-4555-b59c-3de4d4e73d94.text: No, I'm the one who works here.
